ions, and thus yields strong\nsupport to the theory of giant planet migration in gaseous protoplanetary\ndiscs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 20 Jun 2016 18:24:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-06-21"}
