eration slope fluctuations is constrained and in\nthe SSC scenario we constrain the distributions of the correlated magnetic\nfield and flow density variations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 21 Jun 2016 13:41:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-06-29"}
